pageTitle: Product: Chocolate Frosting | Duncan Hines Canada®
textBeforeTable: Servings per Container: 13 Serving Size: 2 Tbsp. (35g) Nutrition Facts Cover and refrigerate any remaining frosting for up to 2 weeks. Cool cake completely. Brush loose crumbs off cake before frosting. Stir room temperature frosting in can before using (cold frosting is difficult to spread). Store unopened can at room temperature, not over 90°F. Notes: Generously frosts two 8" or 9" layers or a 13"x9" cake, brownies or about 36 cupcakes. Directions Sugar, Water, Vegetable Oil Shortening (Partially Hydrogenated Soybean and Cottonseed Oils, Mono- and Diglycerides, Polysorbate 60), Cocoa Powder Processed with Alkali, Corn Syrup. Contains 2% Or Less Of: Corn Starch, Salt, Invert Sugar, Natural and Artificial Flavours, Carmelized Sugar (Sugar, Water), Caramel Colour, Acetic Acid, Preservatives (Potassium Sorbate), Sodium Acid Pyrophosphate, Citric Acid, Sodium Citrate.
